                }
            },
            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "`.nvimrc` and `.exrc` aren't Lua files, so loadstring won't work with these.\r\n\r\nI think it's fine to only support this for `.nvim.lua`, at least for now. As long as that caveat is well-documented.",
