        {
            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "It looks like quick return for a similar condition should be enough (before the first use).\r\n\r\nWhat if such exrc already trusted (before this change) for its directory can do something possibly destructive/unwanted when sourced from subdirectories? I don't know how seriously to take these possibilities, but it's probably good to keep them in mind.",
