        {
            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "Each sourced exrc file will have its own trust value and the user will have the option to view, trust, or not trust each file in the parent hierarchy.\r\n\r\nSo if you open Nvim in some vendor directory, you can choose to not trust the files in the parent directories.",
